    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Many assume the story is about discovering what’s “just right.” Not too much, not too little…but just enough.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Others assume it’s a fable about the risks of wandering off and exploring the unknown, and the upside of staying ‘safe’ at home and ’sheltered’ from what’s outside.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I think it’s simpler than that.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Goldilocks is a story about how there",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "much better things",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "to do with your curiosity than breaking into your neighbors home to discover what they eat and where they sleep.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Curiosity can be your superpower if you let it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}